    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to radioactive dating employing techniques which exploit the properties of the radioisotopic decay of uranium; in archaeology and paleontology, used especially for dating fossilized bones.</Note_Text>
